Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it's this sunny and nice, people grow lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, my old lady stays in bed all morning... Won't even fix breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's what they mean by\N "spring nights know no dawn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)\i1}Note:- The quote is from "Spring Dawn" by Meng Hao-ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's gotten very forgetful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, she left our kid at the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope she still remembers what\N you look like when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't unable to sleep at night, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She sleeps well, snores loud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not. She's so loud that I can't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have medicine for her snoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, about what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? About the snoring medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, about being forgetful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad when someone can't sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Kaji! There's a strange creature in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this crab? You forgot this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They come up from the river \Nevery year around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-was that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Kaji's friend... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just met him. He is the mushi-shi, Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I'm Kaji's mother, Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how she usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always the laid-back type \Nand would forget things a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but from about last spring, she's had \Nsome weird memory lapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'd an unusually large number of customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so I bought Mom her favorite dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These sweets are so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've them from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I eat them behind your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom had completely lost her memory of dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On another day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of selling the ones I don't wear much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I own one like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You cherished it because it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't look good on me, so I never wore it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the kimonos she rarely wore, she forgot only the ones with prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, you scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do a strange thing like that suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A sneeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She had forgotten what a sneeze was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we went to visit \Nour relatives for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji... Who are those two over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Masa and Aunt Mitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's that next to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even her younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than just forgetfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's progressive amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,, And she stays up day and night, working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, she'd often take naps under \Nthat tree in between chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is definitely wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join us, Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing special, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, I want you to write down everything you can recall that your mother forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,, It's a setting for my husband who's away on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A setting for your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's a peddler who travels \Naround throughout the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They say doing this keeps him from\N going hungry during his travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just for peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope he didn't die or anything\N and she has forgotten it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her to stop it because it's wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You reduce your serving to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For whose sake do you think your \Nfather is away on business?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets much hungrier than I do here at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For all the time he's away,\N he doesn't make much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He should take a job nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, he would've come home by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't even written once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you've become absent-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Dad always makes you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:27.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuffing his face and running off like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he just wants his father to be here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband's got nothing going for\Nhim other than being a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he has gotten lost somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His father is not the only one \Nhe's worried about, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You came because he asked for your help, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've heard most of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, did you figure out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For his sake, too... I'd like to ask for your help, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps on, one day, I'll forget \Neven my husband and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I'll even forget that I've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That frightens me more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just about.
